It also requires MANAGE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE permission, [check the documentation.][1]

Usage:

Android manifest:

    &lt;uses-permission android:name=&quot;android.permission.MANAGE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE&quot;
        android:minSdkVersion=&quot;30&quot;
