answers.body_markdown:
Java lexicographically order:

 1. Numbers -before- 
 2. Uppercase -before-
 3. Lowercase

Odd as this seems, it is true...&lt;BR&gt;I have had to write comparator chains to be able to change the default behavior. &lt;BR&gt;Play around with the following snippet with better examples of input strings to verify the order (you will need JSE 8):

    import java.util.ArrayList;

